      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for a total transformation and offers a fantastic foundation for anyone looking to roll up their sleeves. While it's in poor condition and needs a fair amount of work to get back to its prime, it represents a budget-friendly entry point for a dedicated restorer. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
